This paper deals with reasoning in description logics, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also discusses optimization techniques for dealing with terminologies, which involves logical reasoning and deduction (cs.LO). The paper also mentions subsumption reasoning, which is a fundamental problem in description logics (cs.DL). The paper also discusses implementation of systems, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper deals with formal frameworks and proofs, which are topics in programming languages (cs.PL).
